TEXT.S: = Mb'ala = Gaga mniq Nantowseyn Jnaysyang ka alang mb'ala. 142 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 449 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 86% niqan 385 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 14% niqan 64 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal 77%, Seejiq/Seediq/Seejiq/Seejiq/Sediq 5%, Bunun 2%, Amis 1%, Cou 1%.
